"There has been no report of any human health-related issues linked to the consumption of affected tilapia from any of the affected countries since the emergence of TiLV. Looking at fish viruses overall, including TiLV, there is no evidence for a fish virus causing disease in humans." http://pubs.iclarm.net/resource_centre/FISH-2017-03.pdf. - Mod.CRD

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map of the Philippines can be accessed at https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=5463998,4143.]
